<DIV1 TYPE="dedication">
<PB N="iii" REF="2">
<HEAD>DEDICATION TO Mr. PRESTON's Pupil.</HEAD>
<OPENER><SALUTE>MADAM,</SALUTE></OPENER>
<P>GRatitude and Propriety alike induce me to dedicate the&s;e Let|ters to you, to whom they were originally addre&s;&s;ed. From you I received the Permi&s;&s;ion to publi&s;h them, and to you they naturally belong.</P>
<P><PB N="iv" REF="3">Be plea&s;ed to con&s;ider this Dedi|cation a Tribute to Mr. Pre&s;ton, (who&s;e Life was &s;o e&s;&s;ential, and who&s;e Memory is &s;o dear to you) as well as a Token of the continual Re|gard of</P>
